now you should know how you can extends parent class into the child class using two keywords; extends(extends the parent class into the child class),super(means take the properties from the parent that against that property)
ex;
1.

In this exercise, you will begin to create the Nurse class as a child of the HospitalEmployee class. The Nurse class has the following properties and methods:
Nurse

    Properties: _name, _remainingVacationDays, _certifications
    Methods: .takeVacationDays(), .addCertification()

Under HospitalEmployee, create an empty class named Nurse that extends HospitalEmployee.
